Section A – Role and Company Context

[01:10] Interviewer: What is your current job role?

[01:30] Participant P04: I work as an Operations Supervisor in a distribution company. I have been in this role for nearly five years. My job is to supervise staff, organise daily work, solve operational issues and make sure everything runs smoothly.

[03:00] Interviewer: Which industry does your company work in?

